item.title: CVE-2019-10428|2024-08-04T22:24:17.467Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20aqua%20security%20scanner%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Aqua Security Scanner Plugin 3.0.17 and earlier transmitted configured credentials in plain text as part of the global Jenkins configuration form, potentially resulting in their exposure.
